            </section>
            
            <!-- User Guide -->
            <section class="guide-section fade-in delay-2">
                <h2>User Guide</h2>
                
                <div class="guide-step">
                    <h3><span class="step-number">1</span> Getting Started</h3>
                    <p>To begin using the CRFV Event System, follow these initial setup steps:</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2 pl-6 list-disc">
                        <li>Log in using your administrator credentials</li>
                        <li>Configure your organization settings under Profile > Settings</li>
                        <li>Add team members and assign roles</li>
                        <li>Set up your default event template</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="guide-step">
                    <h3><span class="step-number">2</span> Creating an Event</h3>
                    <p>Create a new event in just a few steps:</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2 pl-6 list-disc">
                        <li>Navigate to the "Create Event" page</li>
                        <li>Enter event details: name, date, location, description</li>
                        <li>Add sessions, speakers, and sponsors</li>
                        <li>Configure registration settings and ticket types</li>
                        <li>Publish your event to make it visible to participants</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="guide-step">
                    <h3><span class="step-number">3</span> Managing Registrations</h3>
                    <p>Efficiently handle participant registrations:</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2 pl-6 list-disc">
                        <li>Use the "Register" page to add participants manually</li>
                        <li>Import participants from CSV/Excel files</li>
                        <li>Set up automated confirmation emails</li>
                        <li>Track registration status and send reminders</li>
                        <li>Manage waitlists for popular events</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="guide-step">
                    <h3><span class="step-number">4</span> Tracking Attendance</h3>
                    <p>Streamline your check-in process:</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2 pl-6 list-disc">
                        <li>Use the "Attendance" page for real-time check-in</li>
                        <li>Scan QR codes from registration emails</li>
                        <li>Search participants by name for manual check-in</li>
                        <li>View attendance status for each session</li>
                        <li>Generate attendance certificates</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="guide-step">
                    <h3><span class="step-number">5</span> Generating Reports</h3>
                    <p>Access valuable insights from your event data:</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2 pl-6 list-disc">
                        <li>Navigate to the "Reports" section</li>
                        <li>Select from pre-built report templates</li>
                        <li>Customize date ranges and filters</li>
                        <li>Export reports to Excel, PDF, or CSV</li>
                        <li>Schedule automatic report delivery</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <!-- FAQs -->
            <section class="faq-container fade-in delay-3">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                        How do I reset my password?
                        <i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>If you've forgotten your password, click the "Forgot Password" link on the login page. You'll receive an email with instructions to reset your password. If you don't receive the email within 5 minutes, check your spam folder or contact support.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                        Can I customize the registration form?
                        <i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes! In the event creation settings, navigate to the "Registration" tab where you can add custom fields, change field order, make fields required/optional, and even create conditional fields that appear based on previous answers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                        How many participants can I register for an event?
                        <i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>There is no set limit to the number of participants you can register. For events with more than 5,000 attendees, we recommend contacting our support team for performance optimization tips.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                        Can I integrate with other calendar systems?
                        <i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, CRFV supports integration with Google Calendar, Outlook Calendar, and Apple Calendar. You can enable calendar integration in your account settings under "Integrations".</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                        How secure is my event data?
                        <i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Security is our top priority. We use bank-level 256-bit encryption for all data transmission and storage. Regular security audits, two-factor authentication, and role-based access controls ensure your data remains protected.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
